---
title: MyAIStorybook FYP-2 — Sequence Diagram: Story Generation with TTS/STT
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant API as FastAPI (main.py)
    participant PA as PromptAgent
    participant DA as DirectorAgent
    participant WA as WriterAgent
    participant RA as ReviewerAgent
    participant EA as EditorAgent
    participant IA as ImageAgent
    participant OM as OllamaManager
    participant EVA as EvaluationAgent (Async)
    participant TTS as TTSManager
    participant FS as FileSystem

    Note over User,FS: === User Input Phase ===

    alt Voice Input
        User->>FE: Click voice button, speak prompt
        FE->>API: POST /api/stt (WAV file)
        API->>API: WhisperSTTManager.transcribe_audio()
        API-->>FE: {text: transcribed_text}
        FE->>FE: Pre-fill prompt field
    end

    User->>FE: Submit prompt (text/genre/style/mode)
    FE->>API: POST /api/generate {prompt, mode, genre, style, generate_images, user_photo?}

    Note over API,PA: === Validation Phase ===
    API->>PA: process_prompt(user_prompt)
    PA->>PA: Validate length, classify, ContentSafety check
    PA-->>API: {enhanced_prompt, prompt_type}
    alt Invalid/Nonsense
        API-->>FE: HTTP 400 error
    end

    Note over DA,EA: === Story Generation Phase ===
    API->>DA: create_story(enhanced_prompt, genre, style, length)
    DA->>WA: generate_story(prompt)
    WA-->>WA: Call Ollama LLM (retry up to 2x)
    WA-->>DA: story_draft {title, setting, characters, scenes[]}

    DA->>RA: review_story(story_draft)
    RA-->>DA: reviewed_story

    DA->>EA: edit_story(reviewed_story)
    EA->>EA: export_pdf(story_data) - open-book layout
    EA->>FS: Save PDF to generated/exports/
    EA-->>DA: final_story, pdf_path

    Note over IA,OM: === Image Generation Phase ===
    opt generate_images = true
        DA->>OM: pause_ollama()
        OM-->>DA: Ollama paused (GPU freed)
        loop For each scene
            alt Personalized Mode
                DA->>IA: PersonalizedImageAgent.generate_image(desc, user_photo)
                IA-->>IA: IP-Adapter FaceID embedding
                IA-->>IA: POST /sdapi/v1/txt2img (512x512)
                IA-->>IA: POST /sdapi/v1/img2img (768x768)
            else Simple Mode
                DA->>IA: ImageAgent.generate_image(desc)
                IA-->>IA: txt2img + img2img WebUI API
            end
            IA->>FS: Save PNG to generated/images/
            IA-->>DA: image_path
        end
        DA->>OM: resume_ollama()
    end

    Note over API,EVA: === Save & Return Phase ===
    DA->>FS: Save story JSON
    DA-->>API: final_story (with image paths)

    API-->>EVA: Launch async subprocess (evaluation_agent.py)
    Note right of EVA: Async: CLIP, SentenceTransformer,<br/>Flesch-Kincaid, InsightFace,<br/>Story Structure → save JSON

    API-->>FE: {story_json, pdf_path, status: success}
    FE->>FE: Render open-book UI

    Note over User,TTS: === TTS Narration Phase ===
    User->>FE: Click Play on scene page
    FE->>API: POST /api/tts {story_id, scene_number, voice}
    API->>TTS: generate_audio(text, story_id, scene_n, voice)
    alt Cache miss
        TTS-->>TTS: Run Piper TTS subprocess (PowerShell)
        TTS->>FS: Save WAV to generated/audio/
    end
    TTS-->>API: relative_audio_path
    API-->>FE: {audio_path}
    FE->>FE: Play WAV audio
